              <span id="reviewTextContainer32023168" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2576484486723355796">&quot;It&apos;s not about you.&quot;<br/><br/>Changed my life.<br/><br/>I took Warren&apos;s challenge and found that I was not where I should have been. Paradoxically, I was at that time employed by a Christian ministry highly regarded by many (and vilified by some), but I knew--I knew--that wasn&apos;t where I was <i>supposed</i> to be. So, I quit my job and sought a new direction. <br/><br/>Not there yet by a long shot, but thanks to Rick Warren I&apos;m on my way.</span>
  <span id="freeText2576484486723355796" style="display:none">"It's not about you."<br /><br />Changed my life.<br /><br />I took Warren's challenge and found that I was not where I should have been. Paradoxically, I was at that time employed by a Christian ministry highly regarded by many (and vilified by some), but I knew--I knew--that wasn't where I was <i>supposed</i> to be. So, I quit my job and sought a new direction. <br /><br />Not there yet by a long shot, but thanks to Rick Warren I'm on my way.</span>
