          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780310205715" href="/book/show/115953.The_Purpose_Driven_Life">review of another edition</a>

          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Ruth</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4268487-dustin?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4268487-dustin?shelf=spiritual">spiritual</a>, 
