<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer3595270178688470445">Richard Duane Warren.<br/><br/>As philanthropists, Rick and Kay Warren give away 90 percent of their income through three foundations: Acts of Mercy, which serves those infected and affected by AIDS; Equipping the Church, which trains church leaders in developing countries; and The Global PEACE Fund, which fights poverty, disease, and illiteracy.<br/></span>

</div>
